            . I had some boots stolen; on 14th of February the pawnbroker sent to me; I discovered that they belonged to Mr. Cowen by the mark at the bottom.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18090215-123-person1114">
                  JAMES 
                  HULME
